`email-provider.ts` is the extracted email implementation (used to be inline in notification-service). It implements the new `NotificationProvider` interface.

`sms-provider.ts` is brand new — adds SMS support via Twilio, also implements `NotificationProvider`.

`notifications.ts` (the API layer) wires up SMS for a new `/sms-notify` endpoint that didn't exist before. The existing `/notify` endpoint still uses email.

`types/notification.ts` adds the SMS variant to the discriminated union of notification types.

